OL,6,FA football fan has been charged in
OL,7,Frelation to tragedy chanting at Old
OL,8,FTrafford.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) was
OL,11,Fcalled in to investigate a number of
OL,12,Freports of tragedy chanting after the
OL,13,FFA Cup Quarter Final between
OL,14,FManchester United and Liverpool on
OL,15,FSunday 17 March.
OL,17,FOfficers in relation to pyrotechnics.
