OL,6,FFollowing the initial arrests GMP say
OL,7,FMichael Bernard Avery, 44, from
OL,8,FManchester, has now been charged with
OL,9,FSection 4a of the Public Order Act
OL,10,F1986. He has since been bailed.
OL,12,FThe charge follows an investigation by
OL,13,FGMP's Specialist Operational football
OL,14,Finvestigation team after a video was
OL,15,Fshared of a man in the home section of
OL,16,Fthe Old Trafford crowd.
