OL,6,FOther reports continue to be
OL,7,Finvestigated including a video of
OL,8,Falleged tragedy chants in the
OL,9,FLiverpool section of the ground,
OL,10,Fofficers added.
OL,12,FChief Inspector Jamie Collins, Silver
OL,13,FCommander for the event said: "Our
OL,14,Finvestigation into this fixture in
OL,15,Frelation to supporter conduct is
OL,16,Fongoing and continuing at pace and we
OL,17,Fencourage members of the public to
OL,18,Fcarry on reporting incidents so we can
OL,19,Finvestigate.
