OL,6,F"We are reiterating the message that
OL,7,Fany kind of gesture or comments from
OL,8,Fany supporters to other clubs in
OL,9,Frelation to tragedy chanting will not
OL,10,Fbe tolerated and is completely
OL,11,Funacceptable.
OL,13,F"I would also like this to be a strong
OL,14,Fwarning for any supporters attending
OL,15,Ffuture fixtures in Greater Manchester,
OL,16,Fincluding the up-and-coming Premier
OL,17,FLeague fixture between these two
OL,18,Fclubs, that if you engage in this
OL,19,Fbehaviour GMP officers will do
OL,20,Feverything possible to bring you in
OL,21,Ffront of the courts.
